Package uav.generic.hardware.sensors

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Attitude
    The class models the attitude of the drone (pitch, yaw, roll).
    Barometer
    The class models the drone barometer (relative altitude, absolute altitude).
    Battery
    The class models drone battery (data obtained through power module).
    GPS
    The class models drone GPS (data obtained via GPS).
    GPSInfo
    The class models some drone GPS information (data obtained through GPS).
    SensorUAV
    The class models some drone sensors (heading, groundspeed, airspeed).
    Sonar
    The class models sonar sensor
    StatusUAV
    The class models drone status (mode, systemstatus, armed, isArmable, ekfOk).
    Temperature
    The class models the temperature sensor.
    Velocity
    The class models the drone speed sensor.
